- The "config" object contains the "action" object's configuration (command, args, etc).
- The "condition" object contains the "condition" object's configuration (type, condition, message).
- The "loop" object contains the "loop" object's configuration (count, step, next).
- The "next" object contains the "next" object's configuration (command, args, etc).
- The "id", "name", "type", and "config" are the same as the input JSON object.
- The "condition" and "loop" objects have the same configuration as the input JSON object.
- The "next" object has the same configuration as the input JSON object.

